{
  "stem": "10162.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 236.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So once, they took us to the side of the road.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were supposed to wait for something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they brought some band from someplace.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know it was a-- it was also an inmates band.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it wasn't from that part of Auschwitz where we were because we didn't know this-- we forgot already there is such a thing as music.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember just we were sitting there, sitting there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It seemed like all day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were so weak, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We just can't sit up straight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then suddenly, a delegation comes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it's like with Swiss Red Cross or something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I just knew this was Swiss Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they just march fast through in the middle of the road.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I figured, they will have to talk to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They will have to ask something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They will have to look.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But nobody did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This was just-- when I look back, then I had a sense that this was something very strange, but it was like Fellini-esque scene.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They just march through, the Red Cross and the delegation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then we went back to the same.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Toward the fall, one day, Mengele, who used to come many times just to look over us and to, you know, to select-- find-- try to find twins.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was always checking the craniums.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Came over and selected a few-- you, you, you, you, you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know where we were going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we went to another part of-- of Auschwitz and they gave us some kind of a uniform, a gray dress.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was a number on it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we-- you know, we knew it's something very-- something just good can happen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because we didn't have a number in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't even-- we weren't even in anybody's, you know, bookkeeping.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We weren't even processed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were just meat, fodder to go from one place into the-- into the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we got this dress with a number.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we were put in cattle cars again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were-- it wasn't such a long ride, and it wasn't such a bad ride.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, everything a little better seemed like wonderful at that point.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they took us to-- from Auschwitz, Poland, to-- toward the western part of Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we went into this-- what's called lager Allendorf.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No, lager Munchmuhle, I'm sorry-- Fabrik Allendorf.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Munchmuhle.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "M-U-N-C-H-M-U-H-L-E-- two dots on the U.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And these ordinary barracks, they had bunk beds in it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, we really thought we arrived in heaven-- paradise, paradise.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we got some meal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And for about two or three weeks-- because we were able to walk, but we were still too weak to do anything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So for about two or three weeks, we would get some kind of a meal maybe twice a day or even three times a day, some breakfast, something.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We just couldn't believe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What are they doing this?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have to work or anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So at the end of this period, whatever it was, they took us over to Fabrik Allendorf, which was about, I don't know, maybe an hour walk through this pine forest to a very, very large underground factory complex, which I know now was owned by Dynamit Nobel.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was one of the largest ammunition factories of Nazi Germany, grenade and-- and bomb factories.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
